Emits a {Transfer} event."},"setApprovalForAll(address,bool)":{"details":"Approve or remove `operator` as an operator for the caller. This function call must use less than 30 000 gas."},"transferFrom(address,address,uint256)":{"details":"Transfers `tokenId` token from `from` to `to`.
